Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: nouhailler <nouhailler@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-gtksource-5
Homepage: https://github.com/nouhailler/MacroEditor
Description: GTK4 text editor with semantic macro recording
 MacroEditor is a lightweight Linux text editor written in Python with GTK4.
 It provides semantic macro recording, replay, JSON macro storage, and
 search/replace tools in a minimal desktop application.
